OL,3,CFewer renters saving for home deposit
OL,4,Camid living costs squeeze ` survey
OL,6,FCommon ways to find savings for a
OL,7,Fdeposit include reducing discretionary
OL,8,Fspending, cutting back on holidays or
OL,9,Fusing a side hustle to generate extra
OL,10,Fincome, according to the survey.
OL,12,FAffordability pressures are also
OL,13,Flimiting choices, as more than a third
OL,14,F(37%) said they are unable to afford
OL,15,Fto buy a home in the area where they
OL,16,Fcurrently rent or would like to live
OL,17,Fin the future.
