OL,3,CFewer renters saving for home deposit
OL,4,Camid living costs squeeze ` survey
OL,6,FAround a quarter (26%) of renters said
OL,7,Fthey are struggling to afford their
OL,8,Fmonthly payments, compared with around
OL,9,Fone in seven (15%) home owners who
OL,10,Ffeel the same way about their mortgage.
OL,12,FNearly half (45%) of renters said they
OL,13,Fare adjusting their spending habits to
OL,14,Fensure they can continue to afford
OL,15,Ftheir housing costs.
OL,17,FMany mortgage lenders have recently
OL,18,Fannounced changes to their lending
OL,19,Fcriteria, potentially enabling some
OL,20,Fpeople to take out bigger loans.
