OL,3,CFewer renters saving for home deposit
OL,4,Camid living costs squeeze ` survey
OL,6,FJatin Patel, head of mortgages,
OL,7,Fsavings and insurance at Barclays,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Many people dream to one day
OL,9,Fown a home, but our latest findings
OL,10,Fhighlight how renters are finding it
OL,11,Fever harder to save for a deposit
OL,12,Fwhile keeping up with rising costs.
OL,14,F"More positively though, we're still
OL,15,Fseeing savers create strong habits,
OL,16,Fand consider carefully the balance
OL,17,Fbetween getting into the market
OL,18,Fquickly with a lower deposit or trying
OL,19,Fto minimise monthly repayments in the
OL,20,Flonger term."
